headline: 3 Growth Stocks Wall Street Might Be Sleeping On, but I'm Not
summary: Outside of the technology arena, one of the best places to find growth stocks tends to be in the consumer goods space.  Let's look at three consumer growth stocks that investors should not sleep on.  The king of e-commerce and cloud computing, much of the recent narrative around Amazon (NASDAQ: AMZN) has been how the company's cloud computing unit, AWS, has been the slowest growing of the big three and how it has been ceding some market share.
